COMMERCIAL USE DEFINITION:
Commercial use includes, but is not limited to:
  • Selling sauna controllers or components based on this design
  • Offering sauna installation or maintenance services using this software
  • Manufacturing controllers or PCBs based on this design for sale
  • Operating a commercial sauna facility using this controller
  • Any service or product where customers pay for use of this system

WHAT IS PERMITTED (Non-Commercial Use):
  • Building a controller for your personal home sauna
  • Using in educational settings or demonstrations
  • Contributing improvements back to the open source project
  • Using in non-profit community projects or makerspaces
  • Research and development purposes
  • Sharing your modifications with the community

