SAFETY DISCLAIMER:
This sauna controller interfaces with high-voltage electrical systems 
and high-temperature heating elements. Improper installation, modification, 
or use can result in:
  • Fire hazard
  • Electric shock
  • Personal injury or death
  • Property damage

